        prompt="PLANNER PHASE: Research the target codebase at /Users/theb/Documents/Windsurf/zenagent-employer-contact for epic E1-research-agent: Employer Contact Research Agent. MANDATORY: Invoke Skill('dspy-development') before any DSPy design decisions. (1) Read the BS at /Users/theb/Documents/Windsurf/cobuilder-harness/docs/prds/employer-contact-search/PRD-EMPLOYER-CONTACT-001.md — focus on Section 5 (Research Agent Specification). (2) Explore the zenagent codebase: find existing DSPy modules, Perplexity integrations, PydanticAI agents, database models (especially university_contacts pattern). (3) Identify: existing employer_contacts table or similar, Supabase connection patterns, background_tasks integration. (4) Document: file paths, existing DSPy patterns, Perplexity API usage, database schema. Write structured findings to evidence JSON."
    ];

