        downstream_node="write_ts"
        prompt="PLANNER PHASE: Research domain patterns for the employer contact research agent. MANDATORY: Invoke Skill('dspy-development') and Skill('research-first'). (1) Use Context7 to research DSPy module patterns (Signatures, Modules, Optimizers) and Perplexity Deep Research API. (2) Research via Perplexity: how to build an employer contact finder using Perplexity API + web search (not just Perplexity alone). (3) Research contact classification patterns: general vs named_poc, confidence scoring algorithms. (4) Identify testing patterns: how to test DSPy modules (mock vs real API), how to test web search results, how to test contact deduplication. (5) Document: DSPy module design, Perplexity + web search combo approach, confidence scoring formula, test fixtures. Write findings to evidence JSON."
    ];

