        prompt="FIX-IT RED PHASE: Write failing tests for 2 validation gaps. MANDATORY: Invoke Skill('dspy-development'). Read the TS at /Users/theb/Documents/Windsurf/cobuilder-harness/docs/sds/employer-contact-search/SD-EMPLOYER-CONTACT-E1.md. GAP 2: utils/background_task_helpers.py needs 4 new CallResultStatus enum values: CONTACTS_DISCOVERED, ALTERNATE_CONTACT_RECEIVED, CONTACT_VALIDATED, COMPLETED_DISCREPANCIES. Write tests that import these values and verify they exist. GAP 3: employer_research/router.py endpoints are NotImplementedError stubs. Write tests for: (a) POST /api/v1/employer-research/{case_id} returns EmployerResearchResult, (b) Prefect task wrapper calls service correctly. Tests MUST FAIL because the implementations don't exist yet. Run pytest to confirm failures."
